headline: Sempra: Strengthening Backbone Of U.S. Energy Infrastructure With $10 Billion LNG Infrastructure Deal
summary: Sempra (SRE) remains a Buy, driven by strategic asset sales, utility growth focus, and robust financial guidance through 2029.
